rt their produce to the urban areas. “The rural infrastructure upgrades will in the long run increase economic and commercial activities in both rural and urban area,” said Mr. Mwabudzo. if(typeof __ez_fad_position != 'undefined'){__ez_fad_position('div-gpt-ad-constructionreviewonline_com-box-4-0')};He also said that people can now access markets, shopping centers, schools and places they wish to visit easily from their homes. “Gorvernor Mvurya’s administration is at the forefront in initiating and executing development projects that will have positive impact on residents across the coastal county,” he affirmed.